content:
Analyze this project brief: 'Je veux juste que tu crées un employé pour tester et qu'il produise une petite news de 5 lignes sur le climat 
rien de plus, quelque chose de très cours'.
Generate the required team structure.
Respond ONLY with a JSON matching this exact structure. Use short, unique words for 'team_name' and 'task_name' (e.g., 'Backend', 'UI', 'Database'):
{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "ShortTeamName",
      "role": "Detailed description of their role",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "ShortTaskName", "role": "Their specific role"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "Content",
      "role": "Manage test agent lifecycle and verify 5-line climate news output.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "Writer", "role": "Produce a strict 5-line climate news draft for validation."}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

```json
{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "Content",
      "role": "Orchestrate dual-topic news generation and enforce strict 5-line constraint per article.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "ClimateNews", "role": "Draft exactly 5-line climate news summary."},
        {"task_name": "WorldCupNews", "role": "Draft exactly 5-line 2026 World Cup news summary."}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

**Global Status:**
• Scope Updated: v2 requires 2 distinct news summaries (Climate + 2026 World Cup), strictly 5 lines each.
• Architecture: Single "Content" manager deployed with 2 parallel specialist writers to maximize throughput and constraint adherence.
• Readiness: Team structure optimized and locked.

**Strategic Decision:**
• Dispatch parallel prompts to `ClimateNews` & `WorldCupNews` agents.
• Enforce hard limit: exactly 5 lines per output. Auto-reject any deviation.
• Await submission for immediate QC & consolidation.
